#!/usr/bin/perl -Ilib/ -I../lib/

=head1 NAME

upload-server - The SOS API for performing uploads.

=cut

=head1 SYNOPSIS

  api-server [options]


  Path Options:

   --port       Specify the port to run upon

=cut

=head1 OVERVIEW

* Reads servers from /etc/sso.conf or  ~/.sos.conf.

* Allows uploads to be made.

=cut

